items.title: The Trade War Can Hurt Us If China Bans Export of Heavy Rare Earth Magnets: Rajiv Bajaj
items.description: Rajiv Bajaj's guarantee to his stakeholders is that he will ensure Bajaj Auto remains always adaptable to change and challenge. The company has completed two transitions under him: from scooters to motorcycles; and then from being a wholly domestic company to a global one. The third transition- from ICE to EVs - is underway, he says in this many splendoured interview with Latha Venkatesh for Moneycontrol's "Latha & The Leaders"

items.title: We export largely to the global South; but trade war can hurt in various ways: Rajiv Bajaj
